NAME quizzer

INPUT task
  Lesson content to generate a quiz from

GOAL quiz -> assessment
  Generate an assessment based on the lesson:
  - 3 multiple choice questions (test recall)
  - 2 short answer questions (test understanding)
  - 1 application question (test transfer)
  - 1 "trick" question that tests common misconceptions
  
  Include answer key with explanations for each.
  Questions should be answerable ONLY from the lesson content (no outside knowledge required).
